# Claude Token-Saving Shortcuts

## Ultra-Fast Commands
cc = ddev drush cr
scss = npx gulp styles  
cfg = ddev drush cex
login = ddev drush uli

## File Paths (memorize these)
THEME=/Users/ethanteague/workspace/govt/docroot/themes/custom/gov
SCSS=/Users/ethanteague/workspace/govt/docroot/themes/custom/gov/scss
TEMPLATES=/Users/ethanteague/workspace/govt/docroot/themes/custom/gov/templates
CONFIG=/Users/ethanteague/workspace/govt/config/sync
MODULE=/Users/ethanteague/workspace/govt/docroot/modules/custom/gov_general

## One-Word Responses For:
- "clear cache" → "Cleared"
- "compile styles" → "Compiled" 
- "export config" → "Exported"
- "import config" → "Imported"

## Batch These Always:
- Read + Edit = MultiEdit
- Multiple bash = Single response
- Search + Read = Parallel calls
- Status check + Action = Combined

## Skip These:
- TodoWrite for simple tasks
- File descriptions unless needed
- Progress updates
- Code explanations
- Tool descriptions in bash

## Token Limits:
- Grep: head_limit=5
- Read: limit=50 for large files
- Response: 1-2 lines max
- Explanations: Only if asked